{"tid":2246820,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人開左學之後唔知點樣同同學食飯","createTime":"2020-10-17T11:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T13:55:28.000Z","uid":224836,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6e5a5eec6891d910613c134899ba4b66529b77","tid":2246820,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"我食野好奄尖果啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要好食 又要食黃店 就算唔係黃都一定要非藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時同班新同學幾個咁一齊食 <br />\n求其嘿嘿哈哈咁就入間垃圾餐廳食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前班fd就話慣哂 大家有默契唔食藍店垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依加上左大專 識哂啲新同學 對於食黃走藍呢樣野有啲難講出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚比人覺得我好麻煩又要就我咁<br />\n話哂都唔係個個都追求呢樣野又可能人地係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能點做"},{"pid":"92c4d8c9d7c888f05065a46047217f2ac1d94267","tid":2246820,"uid":71508,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔食就冇必要同佢地做frd<br />\n要isolated佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fde43ac691694f07e578dfe1a317c77f41f6e6f","tid":2246820,"uid":316420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你問吓人地藍定黃先啦"},{"pid":"c15cd1c5802d96321dafb7d125e8f1a45d827007","tid":2246820,"uid":235527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T11:17:03.000Z","msg":"不嬲自己食<br />\n唔撚洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a88599ec9ec34c52338dbccf51df370ad167dc1","tid":2246820,"uid":85586,"like":3,"dislike":